description: Greek officials earlier said they stopped 10,000 migrants crossing the land border with Turkey.
title: Greece suspends asylum applications as migrants seek to leave Turkey
title_page: Greece suspends asylum applications as migrants seek to leave Turkey - BBC News
maintext: Turkey is hosting 3.7 million Syrian refugees, as well as migrants from other countries such as Afghanistan - but had previously stopped them from leaving for Europe under an aid-linked deal with the EU.
